latestIgtvVideos.title: DEF-"I" GRAVITY
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Last week was a rollercoaster ride going down. Things were out of control, felt like going back in time.. doing things right. A week full of self doubt, constant escape,  personal setbacks and mostly regrets. "Surviving the storm" is what I would to name that chapter. I learnt a lot in this time period which I thought would be the later part of my life. But amidst all this thing I wanted to create something that would drain all of "this me" and bring out a better version. I resonated a lot with this song by @iameden

In a day we completed this video. Thank you @accompanyingexistence for investing yourself creatively in this. It was a very liberating experience. 

And now the next part is going to be full of growth.

#selfpoetry 
#gravityeden 
#accompanyingexistence

latestIgtvVideos.title: Khwaish (ख्वाहिश)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Every person in their lifetime yearns for several things but its very beautiful when someone desires a human. Everything around him/her is directly or indirectly related to this desire. Completely Surrendering to this inclination is serene and satisfying. The word one can use for the piece of work is "innocent" as the poet, from every prayer he does to the home he wants to make to the laugh he wants to hear and to the morning he yearns, the only constant is the love(human) he desires.

This beautiful poem is penned by my dearest friend and mentor @dhrutikka and I apologize for the video quality, but as they say blame the quarantine. I am extremely thankful to @keyography11 for editing this through scratch and @dhyanmulrav for audio mixing.Hope you'll like it.

#dhruvfaruq #classonnetflix #2yearstoclass

आज शाम इश्क के रंग की बात छिड़ गई
किसने कहा मेरा इश्क लाल, तो किसने कहा मेरा इश्क केसरी, 
अब सबकी निगाहें मुझपे 
बहुत मुश्किल ये सवाल था
पर जवाब देना भी जरूरी था 

मैंने कहा मेरे इश्क का कोई रंग नहीं है 
लेकिन मेरे इश्क का एहसास जरूर बहना है

उसका स्वाद मेरी माशूका के हाथ की दाल की तरह तीखा है

मेरे इश्क की वाणी कड़वी है 
पर निगाहों की गर्मी सी मीठी नींद पक्की है :)
